      "text": "The usual switch is \nOTEL_METRICS_EXEMPLAR_FILTER=trace_based\n\nThen Prometheus + Grafana can display markers\nand Tempo can open the associated trace",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "baseline": 92,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "The usual switch is \nOTEL_METRICS_EXEMPLAR_FILTER=trace_based\n\nThen Prometheus + Grafana can display markers\nand Tempo can open the associated trace",
